summary: Used foretrenty\'s NPC editor to tame the beast that is Mjoll!
descriptionHtml:
I married Mjoll and quickly realized that she had a few, ahem, flaws.

FIXED:

Mjoll walks like a lady.

Mjoll had plastic surgery to fix the gash on her left cheek.

Mjoll has sexy ice blue eyes (contacts).

This mod is a minimal, but effective, improvement of default Mjoll (yellow eyes... really?).

INSTALL:

Copy files to data folder and make sure they are checked off in \"Data Files\" before you load your game... easy.
author: uNiVerse555
